headline: A Strong Growth Profile Gives Boston Scientific Corp. (BSX) a Favorable Outlook
summary: Hardman Johnston Global Advisors, an investment management company, released its “Hardman Johnston Global Equity Strategy” investor letter for the third quarter of 2025.
